metadata.name: METATALES #1 GOLD Edition
metadata.description:
In your hands you hold a comic NFT from **ENCODE GRAPHICS**. All relevant information about the comic is stored in the metadata and you can visit the [ENCODE NETWORK](https://encode.network)Â and check all held NFTs in your profile. There, as the owner of this NFT, you can read the comic and also download it.

**ENCODE Graphics** is a young book and art publisher that actually emerged from the NFT scene and focuses on futuristic themes. The myths of the crypto scene and the digital and virtual worlds have a firm place and are expressed in narrative form and various artistic representations. More information can be found on our [main website](https://www.encode.graphics/). ENCODE was founded in 2020 by *PR1MAL CYPHER*. 

Please check all the traits of this actual NFT to find out who contributed to this artwork.
